1
00:00:05,872 --> 00:00:06,973
That should be enough.

2
00:00:07,307 --> 00:00:08,307
Go ahead and eat.

3
00:00:14,214 --> 00:00:14,881
Eat your ice cream first,

4
00:00:14,882 --> 00:00:16,216
before it starts to melt.

5
00:00:17,183 --> 00:00:19,718
This is your favorite, sesame.

6
00:00:19,719 --> 00:00:20,786
And their fruit flavors

7
00:00:20,787 --> 00:00:22,021
are made with fresh fruit

8
00:00:22,022 --> 00:00:22,956
every single day.

9
00:00:22,957 --> 00:00:23,957
It's healthier too,

10
00:00:24,457 --> 00:00:26,493
and way more convenient.

11
00:00:31,197 --> 00:00:33,566
You never used to let me have ice cream.

12
00:00:34,601 --> 00:00:35,935
Why the sudden change of heart?

13
00:00:42,609 --> 00:00:43,710
Chen Tianyou,

14
00:00:45,578 --> 00:00:47,138
you've been acting really weird lately.

15
00:00:47,714 --> 00:00:49,416
You're always "busy" when I call,

16
00:00:49,849 --> 00:00:52,018
and you keep leaving me on read.

17
00:00:52,652 --> 00:00:53,692
What is going on with you?

18
00:00:56,456 --> 00:00:58,324
Have you lost weight lately?

19
00:01:00,193 --> 00:01:01,828
Oh, so you actually care?

20
00:01:03,096 --> 00:01:04,296
Me?

21
00:01:04,297 --> 00:01:06,532
I've been working on
my thesis day and night.

22
00:01:06,533 --> 00:01:07,700
I'm exhausted.

23
00:01:09,169 --> 00:01:11,504
Eat up. You need to eat regular meals.

24
00:01:12,505 --> 00:01:14,505
Well, you're the one who
stopped looking after me.

25
00:01:16,209 --> 00:01:17,610
You have a girlfriend now.

26
00:01:18,044 --> 00:01:19,813
It's her job to worry about you, not mine.

27
00:01:20,547 --> 00:01:21,747
I'm talking about you.

28
00:01:21,748 --> 00:01:23,283
Why bring her into this?

29
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:28,488
Is it because of your girlfriend?

30
00:01:29,088 --> 00:01:31,124
I bet she's the one
keeping you away from me.

31
00:01:31,458 --> 00:01:32,658
Do you want me to talk to her?

32
00:01:35,328 --> 00:01:37,563
I told you, it's not like that.

33
00:01:37,564 --> 00:01:39,999
It's not like that, and
I'm not like that either.

34
00:01:42,602 --> 00:01:44,571
Then what is it? What's wrong?

35
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:49,409
Once you find a place you like,

36
00:01:49,809 --> 00:01:50,889
you never go anywhere else.

37
00:01:51,411 --> 00:01:53,346
Just like you've gotten used to
having me by your side.

38
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,747
Once you settle on a flavor,

39
00:01:55,748 --> 00:01:57,150
you'd never dream of changing it.

40
00:01:58,051 --> 00:01:59,986
Just like you only ever wanted me there.

41
00:02:02,121 --> 00:02:03,523
But I have my own life too,

42
00:02:03,990 --> 00:02:05,525
so I can't stay with you forever.

43
00:02:07,126 --> 00:02:08,126
When I'm gone,

44
00:02:09,395 --> 00:02:11,115
you need to learn to take care of yourself.

45
00:02:13,967 --> 00:02:14,967
Why?

46
00:02:16,236 --> 00:02:19,472
Because the person
who'll be with you for life...

47
00:02:21,808 --> 00:02:22,909
isn't going to be me.

48
00:02:24,110 --> 00:02:25,678
Wow, did you order every single flavor?

49
00:02:26,246 --> 00:02:27,313
What are you doing here?

50
00:02:28,081 --> 00:02:29,549
I was invited, obviously.

51
00:02:29,816 --> 00:02:30,717
Chen Tianyou,

52
00:02:30,718 --> 00:02:32,478
is this all you're
having for your farewell?

53
00:02:32,619 --> 00:02:34,087
Well, I guess it is quite a spread.

54
00:02:35,155 --> 00:02:37,390
Farewell? Farewell for what?

55
00:02:42,162 --> 00:02:43,763
I'm going to the UK with my professor.

56
00:02:45,865 --> 00:02:47,033
Wait, since when?

57
00:02:47,433 --> 00:02:48,793
How come I didn't know about this?

58
00:02:49,636 --> 00:02:51,271
It's good that he's got goals.

59
00:02:51,571 --> 00:02:53,238
Don't look so heartbroken.

60
00:02:53,239 --> 00:02:55,039
It's not like Chen
Tianyou is your boyfriend.

61
00:02:59,379 --> 00:03:00,680
Even she knew about it,

62
00:03:01,681 --> 00:03:02,815
so why didn't I?

63
00:03:03,283 --> 00:03:04,417
Why didn't you tell me?

64
00:03:05,118 --> 00:03:06,319
It's like she said.

65
00:03:06,886 --> 00:03:08,188
I didn't want to see you upset.

66
00:03:15,762 --> 00:03:16,762
Here.

67
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:18,430
From now on,

68
00:03:19,699 --> 00:03:21,267
take good care of him.

69
00:03:22,402 --> 00:03:23,669
Don't worry.

70
00:03:23,670 --> 00:03:25,270
As his one and only girlfriend,

71
00:03:25,271 --> 00:03:26,991
I'll make sure he's perfectly looked after.
